# substitutions:
#% macro, device, device name
#% macro, name, Object name and gui association name
#% macro, port, asyn seral port number (e.g. ty_40_0)
#% macro, unit, unit number for multi-drop serial
#% macro, ctlsrc, control source (0 = service, 1 = Ion Pump 1, 2 = Ion Pump 2)
